node.text:
... Something in your eyes
Was so inviting
Something in your smile
Was so exciting
Something in my heart told me I must have you.....
Think of all the beauty still left around you and be happy.
Peeing in this sheet-metal urinal sounds like rain on a tin roof..... Absolutely beautiful experience!
I know it's just snow but in So Cal it's a rare show....
Happily.... Everything worked out for the loanly loaf of bread......
It's tradition. So.....
Nature's gender-neutral bathroom.... Get out of yourself and get outdoors!
Circle up the wagons.....
So sad when nobody wants you.....

If you see something that looks like a star
And it's shooting up out of the ground
And your head is spinning from a loud guitar
And you just can't escape from the sound
Don't worry too much, it'll happen to you
We were children once, playing with toys
And the thing that you're hearing is only the sound of
The low spark of high-heeled boys....
Boys will be Boys #toxic #holdmybeer
One is the loneliest number......
..... gonna sing a little bit of these working man's blues

.... never meant to cause you any sorrow
I never meant to cause you any pain....
Strange how hard it rains now....
He's barely covered in snow..... Muaaaaaa haaaaaaa haaaaaaa haaaaaaa.....
Rainy days and Mondays always..... are better with old friends
And so we should ALL show Goodwill..... However fleeting it may be....
Went to see Aaron Lewis tonight at HOB Anaheim. I will never attend another event here. I Love Aaron, but this joint is nothing but a money sponge. They could give a rat's ass about their guests.
Isn't that how it is nowadays?

....now his life is full of wonder but his heart still knows some fear
Of a simple thing he cannot comprehend....

..... and he'd tell you a tale of the old days,
When the country was wild all around,
Sit out under the stars of the Milky Way,
And listen while the coyotes howl.....

..... oh oh, come take my hand
We're riding out tonight to case the promised land.....

...... and all I do is miss you and the way we used to be
All I do is keep the beat and bad company... All I do is kiss you through the bars of Orion
Julie, I'd do the stars with you any time......
